OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with a few spots of
OL,6,Flight rain, and rather dull along the
OL,7,Feast coast. Further west across Moray,
OL,8,Fit will be mainly dry with the best of
OL,9,Fany brighter spells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mainly cloudy evening and
OL,12,Fnight with a few showery outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain spreading north. Conditions will
OL,14,Fbe rather murky around eastern coasts
OL,15,Ffor a time this evening.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FAny early morning rain
OL,18,Fquickly clearing away. Otherwise a
OL,19,Fbright day with sunny spells and a few
OL,20,Fscattered showers, one or two possibly
OL,21,Fon the heavy side in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
